WEBVTT

00:00.381 --> 00:07.267
Add "er" to make comparative adjectives and "est" to make superlative adjectives.

00:15.802 --> 00:17.671
The mouse is small.

00:21.677 --> 00:24.846
The butterfly is smaller than the mouse.

00:28.778 --> 00:32.381
The ant is the smallest of the three animals.

00:36.237 --> 00:38.107
The lion is big.

00:41.862 --> 00:45.093
The bear is bigger than the lion.

00:49.030 --> 00:52.076
The elephant is the biggest of them all.

00:56.173 --> 00:57.609
Taylor is young.

01:01.303 --> 01:03.668
She is younger than Taylor.

01:07.457 --> 01:09.945
She is the youngest of the three.

01:13.712 --> 01:15.272
Tom is old.

01:18.945 --> 01:21.434
Bill is older than Tom.

01:25.245 --> 01:27.982
He is the oldest of the three men.

